Q: 列出在Jamestown中，使用频率最高的前5公务机及其航班数。
SQL:
SELECT
        d.registration,
        count(*) AS num
FROM
        zts_plane_flight a
        JOIN aircraft_details d ON a.pure_reg = d.pure_reg
        LEFT JOIN avigo_nlp_dev.dc_airport b ON a.dep_icao = b.icao_code
        LEFT JOIN avigo_nlp_dev.dc_airport c ON a.arr_icao = c.icao_code
WHERE
        ( b.search_city_id = "1010" OR c.search_city_id = "1010" )
        AND dep_icao <> arr_icao
GROUP BY
        d.registration
ORDER BY
        num DESC
        LIMIT 1;

ORDER BY
